Makefile Madness 2 (for certain values of 2)
             by Prancing Koala
============================================

Dependencies
------------
Makefile Madness 2 requires OpenGL. If you do not have it installed already,
please do so before trying to build and play Makefile Madness 2.

Compiling
---------
1. Change into the source/ directory.
2. Run 'make'.
3. That should hopefully be it!

Playing the Game
----------------
To start playing Makefile Madness 2, run the 'start' command inside the source
directory. There are in-game instructions on the 'instructions' page. You may
also wish to look at the user manual, located in this directory in PDF and text
format.
